description: Lists analysis templates within a collaboration.

parameters.name: collaborationIdentifier
parameters.description: A unique identifier for the collaboration that the analysis templates belong to. Currently accepts collaboration ID.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: The pagination token that's used to fetch the next set of results.

nested_items.name: collaborationAnalysisTemplateSummaries
nested_items.description: The metadata of the analysis template within a collaboration.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the analysis template.

nested_items.name: createTime
nested_items.description: The time that the summary of the analysis template in a collaboration was created.

nested_items.name: id
nested_items.description: The identifier of the analysis template.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the analysis template.

nested_items.name: updateTime
nested_items.description: The time that the summary of the analysis template in the collaboration was last updated.

nested_items.name: collaborationArn
nested_items.description: The unique ARN for the analysis template's associated collaboration.

nested_items.name: collaborationId
nested_items.description: A unique identifier for the collaboration that the analysis templates belong to. Currently accepts collaboration ID.

nested_items.name: creatorAccountId
nested_items.description: The identifier used to reference members of the collaboration. Currently only supports Amazon Web Services account ID.

nested_items.name: description
nested_items.description: The description of the analysis template.
